Individual portfolios on the following tours include lists of participants,
                        brochures, maps, and other publications relating to battlefield areas:
                        Richmond (3rd), 1953; Central Tennessee (8th), 1958; Charleston and Savannah
                        (9th), 1959; Gettysburg (12th), 1962; Louisiana (14th), 1964;
                        Washington--Booth Trail (16th), 1966; Missouri and Arkansas (17th), 1967;
                        Savannah and Charleston (20th), 1970; Stonewall Jackson's Valley Campaign
                        (22nd), 1972; Kentucky Blue Grass (special tour), Fall 1972;
                        Gettysburg--Carlisle (23rd), 1973.
